<!--Main content begins here-->
$cssColumnChild[

You produce the agreed upon coins. Koh-Inrah counts them, and upon finding the amount acceptable, she grins, flashing her black teeth.
<br>
["I meant for the map to be her dowry, but that's... well, she won't miss it too dearly, I'm sure. That girl just keeps doing what she loves, and she never looks back. I'll simply consider it recuperation for lost investment."]<OldInrahLine|
<br>
Koh-Inrah bows in that customary imperial way and extends the map to you. It reminds you of home.
<br>
["Gratitude, davehmar."]<OldInrahLine|
<br>
---
(link-rerun: "Bow and receive the map.")[\
